1
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:09,560
Mother!

2
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:10,400
Mother!

3
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,560
Mother!

4
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,319
Mother!

5
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,280
Mother!

6
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:20,319
Help!

7
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,239
You guys

8
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:42,280
will be in charge of the security here.

9
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,120
Three shifts a day.

10
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,200
Remember,

11
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:47,400
there must always be someone on duty.

12
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,159
Yes, Your Highness.

13
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:50,760
Is that Sui'er?

14
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,239
Mother,

15
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,239
I'm back.

16
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,200
Greetings, Lady Shen.

17
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:58,920
Sui'er,

18
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,040
who are

19
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,359
all these people?

20
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:06,599
Follow me, all of you.

21
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,159
Mother, don't worry.

22
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,080
These

23
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:14,879
are all hired by me

24
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,599
to protect the mansion.

25
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:18,080
This is the imperial city.

26
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:19,439
What could possibly happen?

27
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,000
Your father

28
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,120
is always frugal.

29
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:23,240
Suddenly

30
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,840
there are so many servants at home.

31
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,080
When he comes back,

32
00:02:26,439 --> 00:02:27,520
he will be angry.

33
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:29,319
If my father blames you,

34
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:30,400
just say

35
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,680
it's

36
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,240
my order.

37
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,240
Okay.

38
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,719
As you wish.

39
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:44,520
By the way,

40
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,639
tomorrow is the fifteenth.

41
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,319
The Empress

42
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,879
invited some officials' female relatives

43
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:52,639
to Lingguo Temple to pray for blessings.

44
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,520
Will you

45
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:56,719
accompany me

46
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:58,240
to the temple?

47
00:02:59,199 --> 00:02:59,639
In my dream,

48
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,080
my mother and I

49
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,479
were attacked on the way back

50
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,280
from the Lingguo Temple.

51
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:04,520
Then...

52
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,360
Then can I ask you

53
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:08,439
to take more guards with us?

54
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,479
Are you

55
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:12,199
up to something?

56
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,639
Mother,

57
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,360
just let me this time.

58
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,039
Lady Shen

59
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,919
comes from a noble family.

60
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,120
You must know

61
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,800
the higher the position,

62
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:28,520
the less we can decide for ourselves.

63
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,680
You're right.

64
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,120
Sui'er has been spoiled since childhood.

65
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:34,560
I didn't discipline her well.

66
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,479
She made a joke

67
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,520
on the wedding day,

68
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,599
which damaged the royal family's reputation.

69
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,680
Your Majesty didn't blame you,

70
00:03:42,199 --> 00:03:43,159
which is already the greatest grace

71
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,400
for the Prime Minister.

72
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,280
Shen Suhe

73
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,039
is a good boy.

74
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,840
Your Majesty arranged this marriage

75
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,919
because of that.

76
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,080
I believe

77
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,439
he will

78
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:57,680
be the pillar of the whole mansion.

79
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:00,039
Thank you for your advice.

80
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:01,520
Mother.

81
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,840
Mother.

82
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:14,520
Yuan.

83
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:15,879
Why are you running around?

84
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,040
Mother.

85
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,120
My brother doesn't want me to come to you,

86
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,959
but I want to play with you.

87
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,759
I greet to Your Majesty

88
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,199
and my teacher's wife.

89
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,959
Your Highness is still so humble.

90
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,759
I just taught him for a few days

91
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,680
when he was young.

92
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,120
After that,

93
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,079
he has been calling me

94
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:43,319
his teacher's wife until now.

95
00:04:44,279 --> 00:04:45,040
I'm

96
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:46,240
a little embarrassed.

97
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,959
This is the Prince V, right?

98
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:51,120
Look,

99
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,279
he looks like

100
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,920
the Prince IV when he was a child.

101
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:57,920
Is this

102
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,439
drawn by you?

103
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,439
It's me,

104
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:03,480
my mother,

105
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,680
and my brother.

106
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:07,920
My brother praised me for drawing well.

107
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,560
He said we are a family.

108
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:14,360
Yuan,

109
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,560
my brother

110
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,079
will take you to play somewhere else.

111
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,639
Zhao

112
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:21,399
will leave first.

113
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,399
The fourth prince's mother died early.

114
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,199
Fortunately, the Empress took care of him.

115
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,600
Now,

116
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:36,959
the fourth prince is so kind.

117
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:39,279
If it weren't for

118
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,560
the Empress's age difference with him...

119
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,319
Look,

120
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:44,920
he and Prince V

121
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,560
are more like real brothers.

122
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:20,959
Thank you.

123
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,240
Put it there.

124
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,360
Miss,

125
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,360
did you come to Lingguo Temple

126
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:31,120
with the Empress to pray for blessings?

127
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,319
[The Imperial Consort Dowager]

128
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,040
[doesn't know me at this time.]

129
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,120
Yes.

130
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,199
I'm Shen Yi's daughter.

131
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,120
So,

132
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,639
you're the daughter of the Prime Minister.

133
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:46,040
Are you lost?

134
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:47,920
This is

135
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,279
the forbidden area of the temple.

136
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:51,240
No one is allowed to approach.

137
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,720
You'd better not stay here.

138
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,279
Please leave.

139
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,360
Goodbye.

140
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,079
Mother.

141
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:20,439
You've finished talking with the Queen?

142
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,519
What's wrong?

143
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:27,000
You

144
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:29,399
still act like a child,

145
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,639
not knowing

146
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,439
to pay respects to the Queen.

147
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,560
Fortunately, she is forgiving

148
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,759
and doesn't hold it against you.

149
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,600
Mother,

150
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,680
you know

151
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,600
I've always disliked

152
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,720
the rigid rules of the palace.

153
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:42,759
Just this once,

154
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,079
I promise it won't happen again.

155
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:45,360
You,

156
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,360
can you hide from it

157
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:48,800
forever?

158
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:51,040
I know

159
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:52,879
marrying Prince Rui

160
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,439
to marry Prince Rui.

161
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,519
But now,

162
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:58,920
we need to

163
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,720
think about it carefully.

164
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:02,759
Master's wife.

165
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:03,839
Sui'er.

166
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:05,439
Zhao.

167
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,480
What did I just say to you?

168
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,240
You forgot it so quickly.

169
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,199
Your Highness.

170
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,920
Sui'er just got married,

171
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,560
She may need some time to adapt.

172
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,439
Please don't be too harsh on her.

173
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,439
I wasn't able to attend your wedding

174
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,600
in person.

175
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,519
This is a wedding gift for you.

176
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:26,800
See if you like it.

177
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:33,240
It's from Zhao.

178
00:08:33,399 --> 00:08:34,039
Of course, I like it.

179
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,159
Mother,

180
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,559
it's getting late.

181
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,039
We should head back now.

182
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,320
We'll

183
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,320
take our leave now.

184
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,279
Let's go.

185
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,639
[If this life's fate can be altered,]

186
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,600
[then perhaps I'll never]

187
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,919
[meet Consort Dowager Li again.]

188
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,559
Zheng,

189
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:29,879
I don't care

190
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,799
what your purpose is.

191
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,200
This trip back to the capital

192
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,879
is too dangerous.

193
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,639
I only have one request:

194
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,240
stay out of politics.

195
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,559
But if the court is in turmoil,

196
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:46,240
do you want me

197
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,120
to sit back and do nothing?

198
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,440
But eight years ago,

199
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,399
you said you'd never return.

200
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,240
So everything happening

201
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,759
in the court today

202
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,440
has nothing to do with you.

203
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:58,840
I'm getting old.

204
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,159
If you have any filial piety,

205
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,759
don't let me see you

206
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,279
die.

207
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,159
Yes.

208
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:11,159
Mother.

209
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:23,120
Mother.

210
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,000
I heard that

211
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,879
Consort Dowager Li is in seclusion in Lingguo Temple.

212
00:10:27,399 --> 00:10:28,919
Why doesn't she live in the Residence

213
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,360
but in Lingguo Temple?

214
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:32,360
I also

215
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:34,399
heard your father mention it.

216
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,360
The late Emperor

217
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:38,279
intended to

218
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,720
make the son of Consort Dowager Li,

219
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:41,799
who is now Prince Yu,

220
00:10:42,919 --> 00:10:43,559
the Crown Prince.

221
00:10:45,399 --> 00:10:46,799
Shortly after His Majesty ascended the throne,

222
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:49,279
Consort Dowager Li moved to Lingguo Temple.

223
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,000
Then Prince Yu

224
00:10:52,279 --> 00:10:54,360
went to guard the border by himself.

225
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:55,879
After a long time,

226
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,799
some past events

227
00:10:58,679 --> 00:11:00,000
were just left behind.

228
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:04,840
You must not

229
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,480
ask others about this.

230
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,679
Don't worry, mom.

231
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,000
I know what to do.

232
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,080
What's wrong?

233
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:16,679
Your Highness,

234
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,120
the carriage broke down,

235
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:18,879
and can't move.

236
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,480
Please wait here

237
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,159
for a while.

238
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,559
We'll continue when it's fixed.

239
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:23,399
Mother.

240
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:24,200
Come.

241
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,240
-It's a good time. -Slow down, mother.

242
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,840
I'm tired of sitting in the carriage.

243
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,039
Let's get off and rest before we go.

244
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,879
You guys take a break too.

245
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,000
Slow down, mother.

246
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:32,720
Alright.

247
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,840
Go check

248
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,919
what happened to the carriage.

249
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:38,960
[This place is identical to the one]

250
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,960
[in my dream.]

251
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:42,320
Mom,

252
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,000
we can't fix the carriage.

253
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,080
Let's go back first.

254
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,720
We're close to the city gate.

255
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,399
It won't take long.

256
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,840
Let's go after it's fixed.

257
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:52,840
Mother, if we don't go back,

258
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,120
Father will be worried.

259
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,320
Let's go.

260
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,799
Come with me. Go.

261
00:11:58,759 --> 00:11:59,200
Go.

262
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:11,519
Mother.

263
00:12:21,919 --> 00:12:22,799
Sui'er.

264
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,080
They're just bandits.

265
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:24,759
Hurry.

266
00:12:25,039 --> 00:12:25,440
Take them off.

267
00:12:25,799 --> 00:12:26,840
Give them the valuables.

268
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,159
It's okay.

269
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:27,720
Hurry.

270
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:31,480
Mother.

271
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:32,679
Run!

272
00:12:34,639 --> 00:12:35,279
Watch out!

273
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:40,679
Mother.

274
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:41,960
Sui'er,

275
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:42,720
you go first.

276
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:43,960
Go, mother.

277
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,960
I won't leave you alone.

278
00:12:46,519 --> 00:12:47,080
Go!

279
00:12:50,159 --> 00:12:50,720
[Sui'er.]

280
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,840
[Is he the one]

281
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:49,120
[who saved me in my dream?]
